5db\u05d5\u05d6\u05d9\u05dd \u05d7\u05e8\u05d3\u05d9\u05d9\u05dd|language=Hebrew|trans-title=Eight times the rate in Bnei Brak|first=Aharon|last=Rabinowitz|date=27 March 2020|accessdate=29 March 2020|work=[[Haaretz]]}}</ref>\n# Not included in this data is the death in Italy of one Israeli tourist.<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/82-year-old-israeli-tourist-dies-in-italy-after-contracting-coronavirus/|title=82-year-old Israeli tourist dies in Italy after contracting coronavirus|date=28 March 2020|work=Times of Israel|access-date=29 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n{{portal|Coronavirus disease 2019|Israel}}\n*[[2019\u201320 coronavirus outbreak by country and territory]]\n*[[2020 in Israel]]\n*[[Health in Israel]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category}}\n*[https://govextra.gov.il/ministry-of-health/corona/corona-virus-en/ The Novel Coronavirus]. Israel's government website\n*[https://www.gov.il/en/General/corona_official Coronavirus information and updates]. Israel's government website\n*[https://www.health.gov.il/English/Topics/Diseases/corona/Pages/default.aspx COVID-19]. [[Ministry of Health (Israel)|Israel Ministry of Health]]\n*[https://www.jpost.com/coronavirus Coronavirus news]. ''[[The Jerusalem Post]]''\n\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic}}\n\n[[Category:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic by country and territory|Israel]]\n[[Category:2020 coronavirus pandemic in Asia|Israel]]\n[[Category:2020 in Israel|Coronavirus pandemic]]\n[[Category:Medical outbreaks in Israel]]\n", "name_user": "Chocom", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Israel"}
